-- Ford reports July sales up 5 percent
-- 
-- Tue Aug 3, 2010 12:18pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/08/03/us-ford-idUSTRE6723TL20100803

 

 BANGALORE  (Reuters) - Ford Motor's ( F.N ) July U.S. sales rose 5 percent as demand for high-quality, fuel-efficient products    continues driving growth. 

